{"tid":266984,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人戒左汽水好耐","createTime":"2017-06-02T02:06:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T05:40:39.000Z","uid":55991,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfda2e894d94ce1ec9bc320936f1432b000f573a","tid":266984,"uid":55991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:06:23.000Z","msg":"以前每個星期都飲三四次，出街食飯都飲<br />\n特別係夏天飲得勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到有個肚腩仔<br />\n跟住的起心肝戒左<br />\nSo far兩年幾無飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n而家肚腩真係細左，雖然唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但戒左咁耐真係無心癮想飲返 見到都唔開胃咁<br />\n以前夏天一口喝就想飲宜家都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b751e323ffb569b23386b26836b3b15720a4f25","tid":266984,"uid":86377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:43:50.000Z","msg":"應該都有1年幾"},{"pid":"976b6c411e9cee595d8faba92197d98cb7c8deca","tid":266984,"uid":46036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:46:29.000Z","msg":"戒左年幾兩年唔飲甜野<br />\n以前好鍾意飲 宜家無欲無求<br />\n飲珍珠奶茶都會走甜<br />\n不過冇瘦過"},{"pid":"d7b1a8d5d4b98675a55fc4aa68f9101f42aa52de","tid":266984,"uid":92230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"一直都唔鍾意飲汽水<br />\n反而戒左啤酒轉清酒 肚腩即刻收左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949a66db5f5a73e2d38a6309692d7a22c702514d","tid":266984,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:50:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b79aca410d58e51a51ae744d8a987b4ef4178a2d","tid":266984,"uid":38988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T02:51:52.000Z","msg":"基本上日日飲水<br />\n茶呀竭力卡啦都唔會接觸同飲到<br />\n汽水真係有朋友聚會先會飲<br />\n但個幾月先一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00f3eda