95430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:56:52.000Z","msg":"戒左糖份幾年<br />\n汽水，糖水，甜品，咖啡(走糖) 全部戒晒<br />\n已經慣晒，依家一食小小甜就好敏感<br />\n不過就無左好多人生樂趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d7344d56f89aaeea3dbc492f7c0fcc5d5bcfe3","tid":266984,"uid":38324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:59:38.000Z","msg":"唔飲原味轉Zero已經即刻瘦返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127e888e7050cc64acb1885fd92e20e6f34a8932","tid":266984,"uid":91165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:00:51.000Z","msg":"飲開ZERO不過好難介, 一飲都成支1L拎上手飲"},{"pid":"94f62e1e719fa2cd2f4288274e56f50e800b01fa","tid":266984,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"睇你自己有無做運動姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日日飲甜野食甜野"},{"pid":"874bdbf37be598300ad9e9f848e9eb693c717035","tid":266984,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"唔會刻意唔飲 但屋企唔會放 出去同人Bbq咪飲下囉"},{"pid":"6357c8b687a54880472a9c5f2a5723d2af873bcd","tid":266984,"uid":35313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:07:30.000Z","msg":"鐘意飲汽水又唔想飲甜野嘅巴打可以試下梳打水"},{"pid":"976d1ee9e512d76fb85198654972189f3a2db7b4","tid":266984,"uid":120158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:21:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf2e802e42cd19a1f24d8bca23b0d5f7ed386040","tid":266984,"uid":21672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T05:40:39.000Z","msg":"返工先飲<br />\n屋企飲品得維他奶同奶"}]}